dc_description_s: This data represents high quality wetlands in Wisconsin in 2023. [High-Quality Wetland points displayed in the DNR Watershed Restoration and Protection Viewer. These are unique wetlands and those wetlands with least disturbed or reference conditions. Points represent a generalized area, for legal and privacy reasons. All points are in HUCs that fall mostly within Wisconsin.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data, please visit: https://data-wi-dnr.opendata.arcgis.com/datasets/wi-dnr::high-quality-wetlands/about
